select s.xitor_id as site_id ,s.xitor_key as site_key ,popname.value as "POP Site Type" ,mkt_name.value_char as "Market Name" ,city.value_char as "City" ,state.value_char as "State" from xitor s join config_value_number pop on (pop.key_value = s.xitor_id and pop.config_field_id = id.get('id.Site.cf.SITE_TYPE_POP') /*POP Site Type*/) join attrib_v_table_value popname on (popname.attrib_v_table_value_id = pop.value_number)
join relation sc on (sc.parent_id = s.xitor_id) join relation_type rt on (rt.child_type_id = id.get('id.Candidate.tt') and rt.parent_type_id = id.get('id.Site.tt'))
join config_value_number cr on (cr.key_value = sc.child_id and cr.config_field_id = id.get('id.Candidate.cf.CAND_RANK') /*Cand Rank*/) join attrib_v_table_value prim on (prim.attrib_v_table_value_id = cr.value_number)
left outer join ancestor_p mkt on (mkt.child_id = s.xitor_id and s.xitor_type_id = id.get('id.Site.tt')/*Site*/ and mkt.xitor_type_id = id.get('id.Market.tt')/*Market*/) left outer join config_value_char mkt_name on (mkt_name.key_value = mkt.parent_id and mkt_name.config_field_id = id.get('id.Market.cf.M_NAME')/*Market Name*/) left outer join config_value_char city on (city.key_value = sc.child_id and city.config_field_id = id.get('id.Candidate.cf.CITY')/*CITY*/) left outer join config_value_char state on (state.key_value = sc.child_id and state.config_field_id = id.get('id.Candidate.cf.STATE')/*STATE*/) where s.xitor_type_id = id.get('id.Site.tt') /*Site*/
and upper(popname.value) in ('MSC','CORE') and popname.program_id = :p_pid
and sc.relation_type_id = rt.relation_type_id /*Site->Cand Rel Type*/
and prim.value = 'Primary' and prim.program_id = :p_pid
